#Even number : A number is divisible by 2 and the remainder gets 0 then it is said to even.  Ex:2,4,6,8...
#Odd number : A number said to be odd when it is divided by 2 remainder leaves.   Ex:1,3,5,7...
#Modulus operator(%) : It is used to find remainder.

num = int(input("Enter a number:"))
if num % 2 == 0:
    print(num,"is an Even number")
else:
    print(num,"is an Odd number")
